#

Cold Beet Borscht (Chlodnik)

45 min
$8.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SoupChilledHealthy

Description

A refreshing chilled soup perfect for warm days, packed with vibrant beet flavor and creamy yogurt.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, cooked
  • cucumber: 1, diced
  • radishes: 4, sliced
  • green onions: 3, chopped
  • plain yogurt: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 3 cups
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • hard-boiled eggs: 2, halved for garnish
